          "_name": "features9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features8\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/html\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"3\" max=\"7\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Price\" name=\"showPrice\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Button\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Transparent\" name=\"transparentCard\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#edf5e1\" condition=\"!transparentCard\">\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>3</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/ejcaportada16-695x878.jpg\" alt=\"Tomo 16\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Juegos de estrategias grupales</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">El tomo de \"Juegos de estrategias grupales\" sirve  para ocasiones con más de 20 participantes, un campo grande y personas mayores de 12 años, dispuestos a crear estrategias ofensivas y defensivas. Este tipo de juego es excelente para retar a un grupo de jóvenes, universitarios o adultos.\n<br>\n<br>ISBN: 9968-922-16-1&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$139</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>1\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/ejcaportada17-695x878.jpg\" alt=\"Tomo 17\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Detonadores de Comunicación</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">El tomo de \"Detonadores de comunicación\" sirve para toda ocasión ya que este tomo está lleno de cientos de preguntas y docenas de dinámicas durante las cuales se pueden usar estas preguntas para detonar o profundizar la comunicación entre las personas presentes.<br><br>Sirven muy bien para reuniones de grupos pequeños, mientras van manejando en el carro y quieren pasar el tiempo compartiendo, como sobremesa, o como una actividad en sí para parejas de matrimonios o familias.\n<br>\n<br>ISBN: 9968-922-17-X</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$119</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>2\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/ejcaportada18-695x878.jpg\" alt=\"Tomo 18\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Actividades de Afirmación</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">El tomo de \"Actividades de afirmación\" sirve para aprender a afirmar a la gente. Tristemente no hay que enseñarle al joven a criticar; más bien se le tiene que enseñar a afirmar y animar a los demás. Por medio de estas actividades el participante aprende a dar cumplidos (elogios), aprende a ver lo positivo en los demás y a expresárselo ya sea en forma verbal, por escrito, por un gesto o por un acto de servicio. Las ocasiones de uso son iguales que para el tomo de \"Detonadores de la comunicación.\" \n<br>\n<br>ISBN: 9968-922-18-8&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$99</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "features9-j",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "u5frXzqQM2",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
              ".card-box": {
                "padding": "1rem"
              }
            },
            "@media (min-width: 768px)": {
              ".card-box": {
                "padding-right": "2rem"
              }
            },
            "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
              ".card-box": {
                "padding-left": "2rem",
                "padding-right": "4rem"
              }
            },
            ".card-wrapper": {
              "border-radius": "4px",
              "background-color": "@cardsBg",
              "& when (@transparentCard)": {
                "background-color": "transparent"
              }
            },
            ".image-wrapper img": {
              "width": "100%",
              "object-fit": "cover"
            },
            ".card:not(:nth-last-child(1))": {
              "margin-bottom": "2rem"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#05386b",
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".card-title": {
              "color": "#05386b"
            },
            ".price": {
              "color": "#05386b"
            }
          },
          "_name": "features9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features8\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/html\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"3\" max=\"7\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Price\" name=\"showPrice\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Button\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Transparent\" name=\"transparentCard\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#edf5e1\" condition=\"!transparentCard\">\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/ejcaportada19-695x878.jpg\" alt=\"Tomo 19\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Juegos con Frisbee</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">El tomo de \"Juegos con frisbee\" sirve para usar un material tan novedoso como el frisbee que atrae la atención y despierta el interés en participar. La mayoría de estos juegos se realizan al aire libre, pero modificando el material para que sea un frisbee hecho de esponja o un material suave se podrán jugar en el interior. Si no cuentas con frisbees oficiales, se pueden crear platos voladores de otros materiales para poner a jugar a grupos grandes o pequeños. Es recomendable jugar con personas mayores de 7 años, generalmente.\n<br>\n<br>ISBN: 9968-922-19-6&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$139</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>1\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/ejcaportada20-695x878.jpg\" alt=\"Tomo 20\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Dinamicas de Capacitación</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">El tomo de \"Dinámicas de capacitación\" se usan en cualquier ambiente de enseñanza o capacitación, ya sea un curso, un taller o una clase. Cualquier maestro de cualquier tema o materia ampliará su repertorio de técnicas creativas para abrir y cerrar una clase, para hacer repasos de contenido y para ayudar a los estudiantes a hacer planes de acción para aplicar lo aprendido.\n<br>\n<br>ISBN: 9968-922-20-X&nbsp;</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$119</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>2\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/logo-ccial-v4-isotipo-96x72.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Extras</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><br>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec malesuada id tellus non imperdiet. Donec elementum urna sit amet est feugiat, ac dictum arcu dictum. Quisque commodo in ante eget ultricies. Proin rhoncus velit et mi tempus, in elementum enim consequat. Aenean vitae placerat nulla. Fusce iaculis felis a nulla pulvinar elementum. Donec fringilla est non vulputate commodo. Donec at libero odio. Morbi in pellentesque nibh. Fusce bibendum, ante eu bibendum tristique, mauris purus tempus dolor, efficitur euismod nunc sem in risus. Nullam massa turpis, iaculis sed consectetur at, feugiat faucibus massa. Integer libero ante, consequat ac viverra et, efficitur non nisl. Donec ornare lectus a venenatis semper. Sed congue sodales fermentum. Donec aliquet arcu turpis, in ornare dolor venenatis at.<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$99</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
