          "_name": "features9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features8\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/html\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"3\" max=\"7\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Price\" name=\"showPrice\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Button\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Transparent\" name=\"transparentCard\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#edf5e1\" condition=\"!transparentCard\">\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/portada-cr-297x385.jpg\" alt=\"Construyendo Relaciones\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Construyendo Relaciones</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Cómo construir relaciones en el ambiente del campamento cristiano.<br><br>~ Factores que hacen aconsejable la realización de campamentos<br>~ Tipos de eventos realizados en un sitio de campamento<br>~ El confidente y sus cuatro relaciones: con Dios, consigo mismo, con el prójimo, con la creación<br>~ Siete reglas de oro para el confidente<br>~ Diez normas con qué crear el ambiente para crecer<br>~ Actividades claves del programa<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$139</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>1\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/portada-fc-297x385.jpg\" alt=\"Facilitando Crecimiento\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Facilitando Crecimiento</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Cómo ser un confidente ministrador y facilitador en un campamento cristiano.<br><br>~ El papel del confidente como facilitador y ministrador<br>~ El arte de ser seguidor<br>~ Disciplinando para discipular<br>~ La recreación con propósito<br>~ La consejería bíblica<br>~ Estilos de aprendizaje<br>~ Características de las edades<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$119</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>2\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/logo-ccial-v4-isotipo-96x72.png\" alt=\"Tomo 3\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Extras</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><br>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec malesuada id tellus non imperdiet. Donec elementum urna sit amet est feugiat, ac dictum arcu dictum. Quisque commodo in ante eget ultricies. Proin rhoncus velit et mi tempus, in elementum enim consequat. Aenean vitae placerat nulla. Fusce iaculis felis a nulla pulvinar elementum. Donec fringilla est non vulputate commodo. Donec at libero odio. Morbi in pellentesque nibh. Fusce bibendum, ante eu bibendum tristique, mauris purus tempus dolor, efficitur euismod nunc sem in risus. Nullam massa turpis, iaculis sed consectetur at, feugiat faucibus massa. Integer libero ante, consequat ac viverra et, efficitur non nisl. Donec ornare lectus a venenatis semper. Sed congue sodales fermentum. Donec aliquet arcu turpis, in ornare dolor venenatis at.</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$99</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
