          "_name": "features9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features8\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/html\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"3\" max=\"7\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Price\" name=\"showPrice\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Button\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Transparent\" name=\"transparentCard\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#edf5e1\" condition=\"!transparentCard\">\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/portada-ebc-297x385.jpg\" alt=\"Creando Encuentros Biblicos en Comunidad\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Creando Encuentros Bíblicos en Comunidad</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Cómo crear una serie de estudios que ayuden al acampante a<br>encontrarse con la Biblia reunidos en comunidad.<br><br>~ La estructura de un EBC<br>~ La investigación personal del pasaje bíblico<br>~ Cómo crear comunidad entre el grupo<br>~ Cómo ayudar a los acampantes a explorar y aplicar la Biblia por sí mismos<br>~ Cómo escribir el Manual del Acampante y la Guía del Facilitador<br>~ Producto final: Un currículum de estudios bíblicos, listos para llevar a la práctica<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$139</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>1\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/portada-dpc-297x385.jpg\" alt=\"Dirigiendo Programas de Campamentos\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Dirigiendo Programas de Campamentos</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Una secuencia de talleres para directores de programa.<br><br>Este diplomado incluye los siguientes talleres de un día: ​\n<br>\n<br>* Recreo Biblico\n<br>* Desarrollo Espiritual\n<br>* El Gozo de Trabajar en Equipo\n<br>* Teaming (Haciendo Equipo)</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$119</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>2\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/logo-ccial-v4-isotipo-96x72.png\" alt=\"Tomo 9\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Extra</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><br>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec malesuada id tellus non imperdiet. Donec elementum urna sit amet est feugiat, ac dictum arcu dictum. Quisque commodo in ante eget ultricies. Proin rhoncus velit et mi tempus, in elementum enim consequat. Aenean vitae placerat nulla. Fusce iaculis felis a nulla pulvinar elementum. Donec fringilla est non vulputate commodo. Donec at libero odio. Morbi in pellentesque nibh. Fusce bibendum, ante eu bibendum tristique, mauris purus tempus dolor, efficitur euismod nunc sem in risus. Nullam massa turpis, iaculis sed consectetur at, feugiat faucibus massa. Integer libero ante, consequat ac viverra et, efficitur non nisl. Donec ornare lectus a venenatis semper. Sed congue sodales fermentum. Donec aliquet arcu turpis, in ornare dolor venenatis at.<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-auto\" mbr-if=\"showPrice || showButtons\">\n                                    <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">$99</p>\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
