\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobiri.se\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            Buy Now\n                                        </a></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-2 d-none d-lg-block' : fullWidth}\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>2\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/logo-ccial-v4-isotipo-96x72.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-md\">\n                                    <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Extras</b></h6>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><br>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec malesuada id tellus non imperdiet. Donec elementum urna sit amet est feugiat, ac dictum arcu dictum. Quisque commodo in ante eget ultricies. Proin rhoncus velit et mi tempus, in elementum enim consequat. Aenean vitae placerat nulla. Fusce iaculis felis a nulla pulvinar elementum. Donec fringilla est non vulputate commodo. Donec at libero odio. Morbi in pellentesque nibh. Fusce bibendum